Title : Chuckwalla River
Text : The '''Chuckwalla River''' is a [[river]] in the [[British Columbia Coast|Central Coast region]] of [[British Columbia]], [[Canada]], flowing into Kilbella Bay, which is a sidewater of [[Rivers Inlet]].<ref>[http://apps.gov.bc.ca/pub/bcgnws/names/26769.html BC Names/GeobC entry "Chuckwalla River"]</ref>  The river's headwaters are at {{coord|51|52|N|127|54|W|display=inline|source:BCNames}}.<ref>[http://apps.gov.bc.ca/pub/bcgnws/names/26769.html BC Names/GeobC entry "Chuckwalla River"]</ref>

The [[Kilbella River]] also flows into [[Kilbella Bay]].<ref>[http://apps.gov.bc.ca/pub/bcgnws/names/3835.html BC Names/GeoBC entry "Kilbella River"]</ref><!--with a different estuary maybe? Hard to say from the map; I'll consult BC Names, maybe there's an error here-->

